  <purpose>To create a CRC card, you can begin by writing out a scenario which identifies the major actors and actions which the&#xD;
actors do. Only write out actions and actors specific to that particular scenario. Nouns should turn into the&#xD;
&lt;i>classes&lt;/i> of the card, verbs typically turn into the &lt;i>responsibilities&lt;/i> of the &lt;i>card&lt;/i>, and&#xD;
&lt;i>collaborators&lt;/i> are the other cards with which the card will be interacting with.</purpose>
